
Add, list, browse, and remove plugin marketplace sources.

Usage:
  summon marketplace [command]

Available Commands:
  add         Register a custom marketplace
  browse      Browse packages available in a marketplace
  list        List all registered marketplaces
  remove      Remove a user-registered marketplace

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for marketplace

Global Flags:
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --target string   Target a specific CLI: copilot or claude

Use "summon marketplace [command] --help" for more information about a command.
